      "content": "i don't know if talking to someone will change the fact that i'm getting worse. it's just a cycle. i see them working harder and harder just to keep me afloat and it feels so selfish to keep going like this. sometimes i wonder if it would be a kinder thing to just... not be an issue anymore. would it be wrong to want to stop being a burden?",
